## Push Bindings

# Right 1/3
bind right:ctrl;cmd      push right bar-resize:screenSizeX/3

# Right 1/2
bind right:ctrl;alt;cmd  push right bar-resize:screenSizeX/2

# Left 2/3
bind left:ctrl;cmd       push left  bar-resize:screenSizeX/3*2

# Left 1/2
bind left:ctrl;alt;cmd   push left  bar-resize:screenSizeX/2

# Top 1/2
bind up:ctrl;alt;cmd     push up    bar-resize:screenSizeY/2

# Bottom 1/2
bind down:ctrl;alt;cmd   push down  bar-resize:screenSizeY/2

# Top left
bind 1:ctrl;alt;cmd      corner top-left resize:screenSizeX/2;screenSizeY/2

# Top right
bind 2:ctrl;alt;cmd      corner top-right resize:screenSizeX/2;screenSizeY/2

# Bottom left
bind 3:ctrl;alt;cmd      corner bottom-left resize:screenSizeX/2;screenSizeY/2

# Bottom right
bind 4:ctrl;alt;cmd      corner bottom-right resize:screenSizeX/2;screenSizeY/2

## Maximise
bind m:ctrl;alt;cmd      move screenOriginX;screenOriginY screenSizeX;screenSizeY


## Centred
bind c:ctrl;alt;cmd      move screenOriginX+(screenSizeX-windowSizeX)/2;screenOriginY+(screenSizeY-windowSizeY)/2 windowSizeX;windowSizeY

## Focus Bindings
bind right:cmd           focus right
bind left:cmd            focus left

